node.text:
On this day 27 years ago (May 1, 1994), Ayrton Senna lost his life after his car left the racing line at Tamburello, Imola 🇮🇹, ran in a straight line off the track and struck an unprotected concrete barrier.
On the video you can see one of his masterful laps in Monaco at the 1990 GP 🇲🇨
Rest in peace to the greatest #SempreSenna A legend lives on!

node.text:
The best of “You’d wear a Rolex” ads!
The company produced these iconic advertisements in the 60s & 70s with hundreds of slogans directed to situations in which their watches were being used. The font used for the advertisements is the new iconic “Helvetica”. Can you guess which one is my favorite? #bigtoys

node.text:
Conor McGregor ( @thenotoriousmma ) has taken delivery of his new $3.5 million Lamborghini Yacht 🇮🇹
• Built by @tecnomaryachts for @lamborghini
• Only 63 units made - #12 is Conor’s with reference to his Proper 12 Whiskey
• 63-feet long with two bedrooms
• 4,000 horsepower
• Top speed of 70mph
It’s only right that the highest paid athlete last year rewards himself a bit. Conor reportedly earned $180 million last year. #bigtoys
C: @1.portofino
